Day 1: Starting Jira Series 

As a DevOps I have worked with AWS, CI/CD Pipelines, Kubernetes, Docker and automation tools. One platform that connects development, operations and project management teams together efficiently is Jira.

What is Jira?
It is a project management tool used for planning and project tracking. It helps teams to plan, track, prioritize and manage work throughout the Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC).

SDLC consists of:
- Planning
- Requirements Gathering
- Development Stage
- Testing
- Release
